<L>__{63 milk bar. rue d'isly. outside inside. day.}
<A>__{milk bar, rue d'isly, at the corner of place bugeand. the jukebox is playing full blast. it is a bar for young people. there is much bustle and confusion, much laughter. the girls are making plans for sunday. djamila enters and moves to the jukebox which is in the corner near the door. there are playbills for various theater performances hanging on the wall. djamila stops to look at them and reads the bottom lines. she places the cosmetic case on the floor. rising again she looks around her, and pushes the case behind the jukebox with her foot ...}
